au hc hi, tho lun v m rng quan h trong lnh vc pht trin website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bi cnh nm 2025 chng kin s pht trin vt bc ca WordPress, khi nn tng ny chim gn mt na s lng website ton cu v p o cc i th trong mng CMS.iu ny cng cng c v th ca WordPress trong mt cng ng cng ngh ti Vit Nam ni chung v Nha Trang ni ring.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Chng trnh Meetup nm nay c u t k lng vi ba ch  ni bt:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Ti u Facebook Funnel  Dn li ngi dng v website WordPress</strong><br>Din gi Nguyn Ph Qu  phn tch chi tit cc bc xy dng phu chuyn i trn Facebook, t vic thu ht khch hng tim nng n vic a h v website WordPress  tng t l chuyn i v doanh thu.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>T ng ha sng to ni dung cho website WordPress vi AI v N8N</strong><br>Din gi Nguyn Minh Phng chia s cch ng dng tr tu nhn to v cng c N8N  t ng ha quy trnh to ni dung, gip qun tr vin website tit kim thi gian m vn m bo cht lng v s a dng ca ni dung.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Xy dng website bn sn phm s &amp; Ti u tc  website WordPress trn 90 im Google PageSpeed Insights</strong><br>Din gi Nguyn Xun Bnh Minh mang n nhng kinh nghim thc t trong vic xy dng h thng bn hng s chuyn nghip, ng thi hng dn cc k thut ti u tc  website, nng cao tri nghim ngi dng v h tr SEO hiu qu.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>S kin din ra trong khng kh thn thin, ci m, vi nhiu phn giao lu, hi p trc tip gia cc din gi v ngi tham d. <br><br>Xin trn trng cm n cc nh ti tr  gp phn to nn mt s kin chuyn nghip, y  tin ch v hon ton min ph cho cng ng.<br><strong>n v ti tr cho s kin:</strong><br>&#8211; <strong>Pay5s</strong> &#8211; Gii php thanh ton nhanh chng, tin li (<a href=\"https://pay5s.vn/\">https://pay5s.vn/</a>)<br>&#8211; <strong>YayCommerce</strong> &#8211; Awesome WooCommerce plugins (<a href=\"https://yaycommerce.com\">https://yaycommerce.com</a>)<br>&#8211; <strong>Tino Group</strong> &#8211; Nh ng k tn min quc gia Vit Nam, l n v cho thu, cung cp tn min, hosting, dch v my ch vi gi thnh phi chng (<a href=\"https://tino.vn\">https://tino.vn</a>)<br>&#8211; <strong>HITECHCLOUD</strong> &#8211; Chuyn ung cp cc dch v DataCenter, ngi chm sc h thng h tng CNTT ca bn. (<a href=\"https://hitechcloud.vn\">https://hitechcloud.vn</a>)<br>&#8211; <strong>BNIX</strong> &#8211; Nh cung cp Hosting/VPS/Server Chuyn Nghip ( <a href=\"https://bnix.vn/\">https://bnix.vn/</a> )</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>n v ti tr t chc: </strong>Minh Duy Solutions &#8211; Marketing Agency ti Nha Trang (<a href=\"https://minhduy.vn\">https://minhduy.vn</a>)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nha Trang WordPress Meetup khng ch l ni cp nht kin thc mi m cn l mi trng l tng  cc thnh vin chia s kh khn, kinh nghim thc t v cng nhau xy dng mt cng ng WordPress pht trin bn vng, ng vi tinh thn phi li nhun, minh bch v sng to m WordPress.Org  cao.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Vi s thnh cng ca s kin ln ny, Nha Trang WordPress Meetup tip tc khng nh vai tr l im hn uy tn ca cng ng cng ngh a phng, gp phn lan ta gi tr ca m ngun m v thc y s pht trin ca lnh vc qun l ni dung s ti Vit Nam.<br><br>Di y l mt s hnh nh ca s kin Nha Trang WordPress Meetup 2025</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-4 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2025/06/NTWP-2025-34.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1400\" height=\"788\" data-id=\"1349\" src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2025/06/NTWP-2025-34.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1349\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2025/06/NTWP-2025-34.jpg 1400w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2025/06/NTWP-2025-34-300x169.jpg 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2025/06/NTWP-2025-34-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2025/06/NTWP-2025-34-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2025/06/NTWP-2025-35.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img dec