1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Trong bui hm nay, i din t Code Tt  chia s nhng nh hng ti u web hiu qu v c mc, ng mc ch, t kt qu.  khng ch l vic ti u PageSpeed Web, m l tng th phi xc nh mc tiu dng website vo vic g v cc bc tin hnh ra sao.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-1.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"572\" src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-1-1024x572.png\" alt=\"Tm hiu v ReactJS, NextJS\" class=\"wp-image-1080\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-1-1024x572.png 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-1-300x168.png 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-1-768x429.png 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-1.png 1291w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p> phn chia s ca anh Hong t Melisoft v m hnh NextJS s dng API t bn th ba (nh WordPress REST API), tp trung vo vic xoay quanh m hnh m-un ho, tinh chnh lin tc, to ra nhng nn tng c mc  ti s dng cao. Anh Hong cng  gii thiu mt s kin trc c pht trin v to ra MeliPlatform kh th v, nhn c s quan tm ca mi ngi thng qua s cu hi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mt s cu hi khc v WordPress cng c gii p v trao i kh nhit tnh.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Vic nh k nng cp website WordPress l cn thit, c bit l cc phin bn Minor (nh dng x.x.[x]). Cc phin bn Major th cn tin hnh sao lu trc khi nng cp.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Nn s dng cc plugin bo mt gip hn ch tn cng nh Wordfence.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Vic s dng kt hp gia NextJS v WP REST API c nhng mc tiu c th, c bit l phi quan tm ti i tng s dng chnh l ai.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Xu hng ChatGPT p dng trong cng vic digital marketing.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Vic ti u website ph thuc nhiu vo ti nguyn, chi ph, v c nhiu gii php khc nhau. Tuy nhin, vic hng ti pht trin vi ngun lc u t ph hp l hng i ng n nht cho doanh nghip.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tham gia cc s kin tip theo</strong></p>