(11, 1, '2025-09-02 15:14:19', '2025-09-02 15:14:19', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<h2> CHNH SCH I TR HNG</h2>\r\n<p>Chng ti cam kt mang n cho khch hng tri nghim mua sm trc tuyn an ton, minh bch v hi lng tuyt i. Chnh sch i tr hng di y p dng cho tt c cc sn phm c bn trn website ca chng ti.</p>\r\n<h3>1.  IU KIN I TR</h3>\r\n<p>Khch hng c th yu cu i hoc tr hng trong cc trng hp sau:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Sn phm b li k thut do nh sn xut (khng do ngi dng gy ra)</li>\r\n<li>Sn phm b h hng trong qu trnh vn chuyn</li>\r\n<li>Giao sai sn phm, sai mu m, mu sc hoc thiu ph kin</li>\r\n<li>Sn phm khng ng nh m t trn website</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Lu :</strong> Khng p dng i tr vi cc li do ngi dng gy ra nh ri v, vo nc, t  tho lp, hoc s dng sai hng dn.</p>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-116\" src=\"http://localhost/ekart/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/111ebcfd-8669-4ad0-aa80-71a3350ffa6c-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></h2>\r\n<h3>2.  THI GIAN P DNG</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>i hng:</strong> Trong vng <strong>7 ngy</strong> k t ngy nhn hng</li>\r\n<li><strong>Tr hng hon tin:</strong> Trong vng <strong>3 ngy</strong> k t ngy nhn hng (ch p dng vi sn phm li hoc giao sai)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>3.  IU KIN SN PHM KHI I TR</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Sn phm cn nguyn vn, cha qua s dng</li>\r\n<li>Bao b, hp ng, tem nhn, ph kin i km cn y </li>\r\n<li>C ha n mua hng hoc m n hng</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>4.  PH I TR</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Min ph i tr</strong> nu li thuc v chng ti hoc nh sn xut</li>\r\n<li>Nu khch hng i do nhu cu c nhn (i mu, i mu), ph vn chuyn s do khch hng chi tr</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>5.  QUY TRNH I TR</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Lin h b phn chm sc khch hng qua hotline hoc email</li>\r\n<li>Cung cp thng tin n hng v hnh nh sn phm li (nu c)</li>\r\n<li>Nhn xc nhn t b phn h tr v hng dn gi hng v kho</li>\r\n<li>Sau khi kim tra, chng ti s tin hnh i/tr theo yu cu</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>6.  CC TRNG HP KHNG P DNG</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Sn phm  qua s dng, b h hng do ngi dng</li>\r\n<li>Sn phm nm trong danh mc khng h tr i tr (v d: phn mm, sn phm khuyn mi c bit)</li>\r\n<li>Qu thi gian quy nh</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Nu bn cn h tr thm, ng ngn ngi lin h vi chng ti qua [email h tr] hoc [s hotline]. Chng ti lun sn sng ng hnh cng bn!</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Chnh sch i tr hng', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'chinh-sach-doi-tra-hang', '', '', '2025-09-02 15:53:21', '2025-09-02 15:53:21', '', 0, 'http://localhost/e-learning/?page_id=11', 0, 'page', '', 0),
