(118, 1, '2025-09-02 15:56:46', '2025-09-02 15:56:46', '<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Di y l<strong>cch x pin laptop </strong>theo hng dn ca chuyn gia. Bn c th lm theo tng bc  t c hiu qu ti u nht.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"buoc-1%3A-truy-cap-cai-dat-nguon-dien-(power-options)\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 1: Truy cp ci t ngun in (Power Options)</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Trc tin, bn cn vo phn thit lp ngun in trn my  iu chnh cc thng s bng cc cch sau:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Cch 1</strong>: Nhn t hp<strong>Windows + X</strong>, sau  chn<strong>Power Options</strong>t menu xut hin.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Cch 2</strong>: Nhp chut phi vo<strong>biu tng pin</strong> gc phi thanh taskbar v chn<strong>Power Options</strong>.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-xa-pin-laptop-01.jpg\" alt=\"Cch x pin laptop ng cch t chuyn gia\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Kt thc bc 1, bn  m c ci t ngun nn tng cho cc bc cu hnh tip theo.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"buoc-2%3A-mo-cai-dat-nguon-nang-cao\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 2: M ci t ngun nng cao</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Sau khi vo c giao din ngun in, bn cn truy cp phn ci t nng cao  c th iu chnh chi tit. Trong giao din<strong>Power Options</strong>, tip tc chn<strong>Additional power settings</strong> vo phn iu chnh chuyn su.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-xa-pin-laptop-02.jpg\" alt=\"M ci t ngun nng cao\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Kt thc bc 2, bn  sn sng ty chnh k hoch ngun ang hot ng trn my.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"buoc-3%3A-tuy-chinh-ke-hoach-nguon-hien-tai\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 3: Ty chnh k hoch ngun hin ti</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Chn<strong>Change plan settings</strong> k hoch ngun bn ang s dng  bt u thay i cc thit lp (thng l Balanced hoc Power Saver).</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-xa-pin-laptop-03.jpg\" alt=\"Ty chnh k hoch ngun hin ti\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">y l bc quan trng  thit lp ch  ph hp trc khi x pin. Gip laptop hot ng lin tc m khng b ngt qung do t ng tt mn hnh hay chuyn sang ch  ng.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"buoc-4%3A-thiet-lap-khong-cho-may-ngu-hay-tat-man-hinh\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 4: Thit lp khng cho my ng hay tt mn hnh</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ti mc<strong>Change settings for the plan</strong>, iu chnh cc thng s sau cho c hai trng thi On battery v Plugged in:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Turn off display</strong>: chn<strong>Never</strong></span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Put the computer to sleep</strong>: chn<strong>Never</strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-xa-pin-laptop-4.jpg\" alt=\"Thit lp khng cho my ng hay tt mn hnh\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Sau khi iu chnh, nhn<strong>Save changes</strong> lu li cu hnh. Kt thc bc 4, laptop ca bn s lun bt cho n khi pin cn, khng b gin on do h thng t ngt.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"buoc-5%3A-dung-may-den-khi-pin-gan-can\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 5: Dng my n khi pin gn cn</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Tin hnh s dng laptop cho n khi pin cn khong 35%. Sau  nhn nt ngun  tt my hon ton.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-xa-pin-laptop-5.jpg\" alt=\"Dng my n khi pin gn cn\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Khi my  tt, khi ng li v truy cp vo<strong>BIOS</strong>.  nguyn my  giao din BIOS (khng thao tc g) cho n khi laptop t tt. Qu trnh ny gip pin c x cn mt cch trit . Kt thc bc 5, bn  gip pin laptop c x gn nh hon ton mt cch an ton.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"buoc-6%3A-de-pin-nghi-va-tan-nhiet\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 6:  pin ngh v tn nhit</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Sau khi my t tt hon ton, rt sc ra v  laptop ngh trong khong 30 pht  pin c lm ngui t nhin.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"buoc-7%3A-sac-lai-den-100%25\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 7: Sc li n 100%</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Bc cui cng l sc li pin n y 100% m khng s dng my trong qu trnh sc. iu ny m bo qu trnh hiu chnh pin din ra chnh xc nht.</span>\r\n<h2 id=\"cach-sac-xa-pin-laptop-moi-mua-chuan%2C-an-toan\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Cch sc x pin laptop mi mua chun, an ton</strong></span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Laptop mi nn c sc y ngay ln u s dng. Sau 23 ln sc, c th thc hin 1 ln x pin theo ng quy trnh  hiu chnh pin. Di y l<strong>cch x pin laptop</strong>chun, c bit ph hp vi my mi:</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 1</strong>: Sc y pin laptop n 100%, m bo khng b ngt gia chng trong qu trnh sc.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 2</strong>: Sau khi sc y, bn hy rt sc khi laptop. Tip theo, s dng my cho cc tc v nh nh lt web, nghe nhc, trong khong 2 gi  pin c ngh.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 3</strong>: Tip tc s dng my n khi pin gim cn khong 5%. Sau   my t chuyn sang ch  ng ng (Hibernate).</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 4</strong>: Khi my  tt hon ton v chuyn sang ch  ng ng. Hy gi nguyn trng thi ny trong 5 gi  pin c x trit .</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 5</strong>: Sau thi gian ngh, sc li pin n 100% m khng s dng my trong qu trnh sc.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-xa-pin-laptop-6.jpg\" alt=\"Cch sc x pin laptop mi mua chun, an ton\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">X pin laptop ng cch khng ch gip hiu chnh li dung lng pin m cn gp phn ko di tui th thit b. c bit quan trng vi nhng dng laptop mi hoc  s dng lu ngy.</span>\r\n<h2 id=\"xa-pin-laptop-de-lam-gi%3F\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>X pin laptop  lm g?</strong></span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">X pin laptop l qu trnh s dng pin n khi gn cn kit, thng di 5%. Mc ch l gip h thng hiu chun li pin v hin th dung lng chnh xc hn. Vic ny gip trnh tnh trng pin o khin my sp ngun d cn pin hin th.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Pin lithium-ion hin i khng yu cu x pin thng xuyn nh pin th h c. Tuy vy, x pin nh k vn mang li li ch nht nh cho laptop. Gip ko di tui th pin v ci thin hiu sut s dng pin tng th.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-xa-pin-laptop-7.jpg\" alt=\"X pin laptop  lm g?\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Laptop mi nn c x pin v sc y trong vi ln u s dng. iu ny gip h iu hnh ghi nhn y  dung lng pin tht. Nu khng dng my trong thi gian di, nn x pin xung khong 20% ri sc li. Vic ny gip duy tr  bn ha hc bn trong pin. Theo chuyn gia, nn x pin laptop mi 13 thng  bo v pin.</span>\r\n<h2 id=\"khi-nao-can-xa-pin-laptop%3F\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Khi no cn x pin laptop?</strong></span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">X pin laptop nh k l mt trong nhng cch n gin nhng hiu qu  duy tr hiu sut pin. Khi s dng lu ngy, pin c th gp phi tnh trng sai lch trong vic hin th dung lng thc. Mt s du hiu ph bin cho thy  n lc bn nn x pin gm:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Pin o</strong>: Pin bo y nhng thi gian s dng li rt ngn.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Pin chai</strong>: Bn phi sc pin thng xuyn hn, thi lng s dng gim ng k.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Laptop sp ngun t ngt</strong>: My tt khi vn cn hin th phn trm pin cao.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-xa-pin-laptop-8.jpg\" alt=\"Khi no cn x pin laptop?\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">X pin ng cch gip loi b tnh trng o dung lng v h tr hiu chnh li h thng o pin. ng thi, kim tra v hiu chun pin nh k cng gip bn pht hin sm cc du hiu h hng.</span>\r\n<h2 id=\"co-nen-xa-pin-laptop%3F\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>C nn x pin laptop?</strong></span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"> pin hot ng bn, ngi dng nn hiu chun pin nh k bng cch x sc ng k thut. Phng php ny gip phn mm o pin hin th chnh xc dung lng thc t ca vin pin. Ngoi ra cn gip hn ch tnh trng pin o khin laptop sp ngun d cn phn trm pin hin th.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-xa-pin-laptop-9.jpg\" alt=\"C nn x pin laptop?\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Nu lm dng hoc x pin sai cch, pin s nhanh chai v c th lm hng  cng HDD. V vy, hy x pin ng hng dn v theo khuyn ngh t cc chuyn gia k thut. Bn nn thc hin vic ny mi 1 n 3 thng mt ln  pin hot ng n nh. Sau khi x cn pin, hy sc li y 100% trong khong 4 gi