(126, 1, '2025-09-02 16:14:22', '2025-09-02 16:14:22', '<h2 id=\"cach-ve-sinh-laptop-tai-nha-can-chuan-bi-gi%3F\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Cch v sinh laptop ti nh cn chun b g?</strong></span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Trc khi bit<strong>cch v sinh laptop</strong>sao cho thun li v an ton, bn cn chun b y  cc dng c sau:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Khn mm, kh:</strong>Nn dng khn microfiber  trnh lm xc b mt laptop.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bnh xt kh nn:</strong>Dng  thi bi  cc khe nh nh bn phm, hay cng kt ni.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>C qut bi mm v tm bng:</strong>Loi c nh, lng mm  qut bi trn b mt my v cc chi tit nh.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Dung dch v sinh mn hnh:</strong>Chn loi dung dch chuyn dng, khng cha cn  trnh lm hng mn hnh.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Tuc n vt (nu cn):</strong>Trong trng hp bn mun tho v my  v sinh bn trong.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-ve-sinh-laptop-2025-1.jpg\" alt=\"Cch v sinh laptop ti nh cn chun b g\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Chun b y  dng c l bc u quan trng,  vic v sinh laptop c thc hin ng cch v hiu qu nht.</span>\r\n<h2 id=\"cach-ve-sinh-laptop-dung-cach-tai-nha\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Cch v sinh laptop ng cch ti nh</strong></span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Di y cch v sinh my tnh laptop,  bn c th t v sinh cc b phn mt cch an ton v hiu qu:</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"cach-ve-sinh-vo-ngoai-laptop-sach-nhu-moi\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Cch v sinh v ngoi laptop sch nh mi</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">V ngoi laptop l ni tip xc nhiu vi bi bn v m hi.  v sinh v ngoi, bn c th dng khn mm thm mt t dung dch v sinh chuyn dng. Hoc c th dng nc sch pha long cn,  lau nh nhng.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-ve-sinh-laptop-2025-2.jpg\" alt=\"Cch v sinh laptop ng cch ti nh\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Bn cn trnh dng lc mnh hoc cc cht ty ra mnh  khng lm try xc hoc phai mu v my. Ngoi ra, cng nn dng khn m lau li ton b v my, trnh  nc chy vo khe.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"cach-ve-sinh-man-hinh-laptop-khong-lam-tray-xuoc\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Cch v sinh mn hnh laptop khng lm try xc</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Cch v sinh laptop ng cch c bit l mn hnh rt quan trng. V y l b phn rt d b try xc, v vy cn c bit cn thn khi v sinh nh sau:</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 1:</strong>Dng khn mm microfiber sch v kh  lau bi b mt.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 2:</strong>Nu c vt bn, xt mt t dung dch v sinh mn hnh chuyn dng ln khn (khng xt trc tip ln mn hnh).</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 3:</strong>Lau theo chuyn ng trn nh nhng, trnh n mnh tay ln mn hnh.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-ve-sinh-laptop-2025-3.jpg\" alt=\"Cch v sinh mn hnh laptop khng lm try xc\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Bn c th thay dung dch chuyn dng bng hn hp cn isopropyl pha long vi nc ct (t l 1:1) nu cn.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"cach-ve-sinh-ban-phim-laptop-de-loai-bo-bui-ban\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Cch v sinh bn phm laptop  loi b bi bn</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Bn phm l ni tch t nhiu bi bn, vn thc n v vi khun  v sinh bn phm bn c th:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Dng c mm hoc chi v sinh  qut sch bi trn b mt bn phm.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Dng bng thi bi hoc bnh kh nn xt vo cc khe gia cc phm  y bi ra ngoi.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Vi cc vt bn cng u, dng tm bng thm cn lau nh tng phm.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Bn nn tho v my  v sinh k hn.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-ve-sinh-laptop-2025-4.jpg\" alt=\"Cch v sinh bn phm laptop  loi b bi bn\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Nhng khng c  k nng v dng c cn thit,  thc hin cch v sinh laptop ti nh, c bit l bn phm. Bn khng nn s dng cch ny, v c th lm gy cht phm.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"cach-lam-sach-quat-tan-nhiet-va-khe-thoat-khi\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Cch lm sch qut tn nhit v khe thot kh</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Qut tn nhit v khe thot kh b bm bi s lm gim hiu sut tn nhit ca laptop. T , dn n my b nng v chy chm.  v sinh qut tn nhit v khe thot kh, bn c th:</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 1:</strong>Chun b bnh kh nn, tua vt, c nh.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 2:</strong>Tho np lng bng tua vt (nu am hiu k thut).</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 3:</strong>Dng bnh kh nn thi ngc chiu qut  y bi ra. Ngoi ra, nn c nh cnh qut v khe tn nhit bng c mm hoc dng bnh xt kh nn  thi bay bi bn.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-ve-sinh-laptop-2025-5.jpg\" alt=\"Cch lm sch qut tn nhit v khe thot kh\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Vi nhng dng c n gin v cc bc thc hin cn thn, bn hon ton c th t v sinh laptop ti nh mt cch hiu qu.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"cach-ve-sinh-cong-ket-noi-laptop\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Cch v sinh cng kt ni laptop</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Cc cng kt ni nh USB, HDMI, v cng sc cng cn c v sinh  m bo kh nng kt ni n nh.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 1:</strong>Dng chi mm nh hoc c chuyn dng  qut bi quanh cc cng nh USB, HDMI, jack tai nghe, cng sc.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Bc 2:</strong>Dng bnh kh nn xt nh vo tng cng  thi bi bn ra ngoi.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-ve-sinh-laptop-2025-6.jpg\" alt=\"Cch v sinh cng kt ni laptop\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Vi cc cng c du hiu bm bn hoc oxy ha nh, c th dng tm bng tm cn isopropyl lau nh bn trong.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"cach-ve-sinh-loa-laptop-hieu-qua\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Cch v sinh loa laptop hiu qu</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Loa laptop c th b bm bi, nh hng n cht lng m thanh,  v sinh loa, bn cn:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Dng chi mm hoc c nh lm sch nh nhng phn li loa trn thn my.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Dng bnh kh nn thi bi t xa, trnh thi qu mnh trc tip vo loa  khng lm rch mng loa.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Nu loa b bm bi nhiu, dng tm bng kh  lau k cc khe h hoc l loa.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-ve-sinh-laptop-2025-7.jpg\" alt=\"Cch v sinh loa laptop hiu qu\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Nn lu , khng s dng nc hoc dung dch lng khi v sinh loa, v rt d thm vo bn trong gy chp mch.</span>\r\n<h2 id=\"cach-ve-sinh-laptop-ben-trong-theo-chuyen-gia\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Cch v sinh laptop bn trong theo chuyn gia</strong></span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Bn cnh vic v sinh bn ngoi, phn v sinh laptop bn trong cng v cng quan trng.  m bo my khng b qu nhit, hot ng n nh v ko di tui th</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"co-nen-tu-thao-laptop-de-ve-sinh-khong%3F\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>C nn t tho laptop  v sinh khng?</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Vic t tho laptop  v sinh bn trong nh qut tn nhit, mainboard hay  cng ch nn thc hin nu bn c kinh nghim k thut. Mt s ri ro c th gp phi nh:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Lm gy ngm, v linh kin trong qu trnh tho lp.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Chm linh kin gy chp mch do tnh in.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Khng v sinh ng cch lm bi bm ngc tr li hoc lm lch keo tn nhit.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-ve-sinh-laptop-2025-8.jpg\" alt=\"Cch v sinh laptop bn trong theo chuyn gia\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Nu bn khng am hiu r v k thut hoc cha tng bit qua cch v sinh laptop. Tt nht nn mang my n cc trung tm uy tn nh in Thoi Vui  c v sinh laptop chuyn su. Theo ng quy trnh v tuyt i gi an ton cho thit b.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"khi-nao-can-thay-keo-tan-nhiet-cho-laptop%3F\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Khi no cn thay keo tn nhit cho laptop?</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Keo tn nhit c nhim v dn nhit t CPU/GPU sang h thng tn nhit. Theo thi gian, keo ny s b kh, mt tc dng v khin my nng nhanh, gy gim hiu sut. Mt s du hiu cho thy, laptop cn thay keo tn nhit nh sau:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Laptop chy nng bt thng d khng dng tc v nng.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Qut tn nhit hot ng lin tc vi ting n ln.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">My t ng tt khi chi game hoc dng phn mm nng.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Bn nn thay keo tn nhit nh k t 12 nm/ln ti trung tm k thut c kinh nghim  m bo.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"dau-hieu-laptop-can-ve-sinh-ve-trong\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Du hiu laptop cn v sinh v trong</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Nu gp cc du hiu di y, laptop ca bn c th ang cn c v sinh phn cng bn trong:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">My nng ln nhanh chng, ngay c khi s dng cc tc v nh.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Qut tn nhit hot ng lin tc v pht ra ting n ln.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Hiu sut gim r rt, c cc du hiu nh my chy chm, git lag, m ng dng lu.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">My t ng tt ngun do qu nhit.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Khi thy nhng du hiu trn, bn nn mang my n cc c s sa cha chuyn nghip nh in Thoi Vui.  c kim tra v v sinh ton din, gip my laptop hot ng n nh tr li.</span>\r\n<h2 id=\"cach-bao-ve-laptop-sau-khi-ve-sinh\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Cch bo v laptop sau khi v sinh</strong></span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Sau khi  v sinh sch s, bn cng