(128, 1, '2025-09-02 16:14:22', '2025-09-02 16:14:22', '<h2 id=\"cach-ve-sinh-laptop-tai-nha-can-chuan-bi-gi%3F\"><strong>Cch v sinh laptop ti nh cn chun b g?</strong></h2>\r\nTrc khi bit<strong>cch v sinh laptop</strong>sao cho thun li v an ton, bn cn chun b y  cc dng c sau:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Khn mm, kh:</strong>Nn dng khn microfiber  trnh lm xc b mt laptop.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Bnh xt kh nn:</strong>Dng  thi bi  cc khe nh nh bn phm, hay cng kt ni.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>C qut bi mm v tm bng:</strong>Loi c nh, lng mm  qut bi trn b mt my v cc chi tit nh.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Dung dch v sinh mn hnh:</strong>Chn loi dung dch chuyn dng, khng cha cn  trnh lm hng mn hnh.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Tuc n vt (nu cn):</strong>Trong trng hp bn mun tho v my  v sinh bn trong.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-ve-sinh-laptop-2025-1.jpg\" alt=\"Cch v sinh laptop ti nh cn chun b g\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\nChun b y  dng c l bc u quan trng,  vic v sinh laptop c thc hin ng cch v hiu qu nht.\r\n<h2 id=\"cach-ve-sinh-laptop-dung-cach-tai-nha\"><strong>Cch v sinh laptop ng cch ti nh</strong></h2>\r\nDi y cch v sinh my tnh laptop,  bn c th t v sinh cc b phn mt cch an ton v hiu qu:\r\n<h3 id=\"cach-ve-sinh-vo-ngoai-laptop-sach-nhu-moi\"><strong>Cch v sinh v ngoi laptop sch nh mi</strong></h3>\r\nV ngoi laptop l ni tip xc nhiu vi bi bn v m hi.  v sinh v ngoi, bn c th dng khn mm thm mt t dung dch v sinh chuyn dng. Hoc c th dng nc sch pha long cn,  lau nh nhng.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-ve-sinh-laptop-2025-2.jpg\" alt=\"Cch v sinh laptop ng cch ti nh\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\nBn cn trnh dng lc mnh hoc cc cht ty ra mnh  khng lm try xc hoc phai mu v my. Ngoi ra, cng nn dng khn m lau li ton b v my, trnh  nc chy vo khe.\r\n<h3 id=\"cach-ve