hun b bnh kh nn, tua vt, c nh.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bc 2:</strong>Tho np lng bng tua vt (nu am hiu k thut).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bc 3:</strong>Dng bnh kh nn thi ngc chiu qut  y bi ra. Ngoi ra, nn c nh cnh qut v khe tn nhit bng c mm hoc dng bnh xt kh nn  thi bay bi bn.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-ve-sinh-laptop-2025-5.jpg\" alt=\"Cch lm sch qut tn nhit v khe thot kh\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\nVi nhng dng c n gin v cc bc thc hin cn thn, bn hon ton c th t v sinh laptop ti nh mt cch hiu qu.\r\n<h3 id=\"cach-ve-sinh-cong-ket-noi-laptop\"><strong>Cch v sinh cng kt ni laptop</strong></h3>\r\nCc cng kt ni nh USB, HDMI, v cng sc cng cn c v sinh  m bo kh nng kt ni n nh.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bc 1:</strong>Dng chi mm nh hoc c chuyn dng  qut bi quanh cc cng nh USB, HDMI, jack tai nghe, cng sc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bc 2:</strong>Dng bnh kh nn xt nh vo tng cng  thi bi bn ra ngoi.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-ve-sinh-laptop-2025-6.jpg\" alt=\"Cch v sinh cng kt ni laptop\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\nVi cc cng c du hiu bm bn hoc oxy ha nh, c th dng tm bng tm cn isopropyl lau nh bn trong.\r\n<h3 id=\"cach-ve-sinh-loa-laptop-hieu-qua\"><strong>Cch v sinh loa laptop hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\nLoa laptop c th b bm bi, nh hng n cht lng m thanh,  v sinh loa, bn cn:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dng chi mm hoc c nh lm sch nh nhng phn li loa trn thn my.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng bnh kh nn thi bi t xa, trnh thi qu mnh trc tip vo loa  khng lm rch mng loa.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nu loa b bm bi nhiu, dng tm bng kh  lau k cc khe h hoc l loa.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-ve-sinh-laptop-2025-7.jpg\" alt=\"Cch v sinh loa laptop hiu qu\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\nNn lu , khng s dng nc hoc dung dch lng khi v sinh loa, v rt d thm vo bn trong gy chp mch.\r\n<h2 id=\"cach-ve-sinh-laptop-ben-trong-theo-chuyen-gia\"><strong>Cch v sinh laptop bn trong theo chuyn gia</strong></h2>\r\nBn cnh vic v sinh bn ngoi, phn v sinh laptop bn trong cng v cng quan trng.  m bo my khng b qu nhit, hot ng n nh v ko di tui th\r\n<h3 id=\"co-nen-tu-thao-laptop-de-ve-sinh-khong%3F\"><strong>C nn t tho laptop  v sinh khng?</strong></h3>\r\nVic t tho laptop  v sinh bn trong nh qut tn nhit, mainboard hay  cng ch nn thc hin nu bn c kinh nghim k thut. Mt s ri ro c th gp phi nh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Lm gy ngm, v linh kin trong qu trnh tho lp.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chm linh kin gy chp mch do tnh in.</li>\r\n 	<li>Khng v sinh ng cch lm bi bm ngc tr li hoc lm lch keo tn nhit.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cach-ve-sinh-laptop-2025-8.jpg\" alt=\"Cch v sinh laptop bn trong theo chuyn gia\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\nNu bn khng am hiu r v k thut hoc cha tng bit qua cch v sinh laptop. Tt nht nn mang my n cc trung tm uy tn nh in Thoi Vui  c v sinh laptop chuyn su. Theo ng quy trnh v tuyt i gi an ton cho thit b.\r\n<h3 id=\"khi-nao-can-thay-keo-tan-nhiet-cho-laptop%3F\"><strong>Khi no cn thay keo tn nhit cho laptop?</strong></h3>\r\nKeo tn nhit c nhim v dn nhit t CPU/GPU sang h thng tn nhit. Theo thi gian, keo ny s b kh, mt tc dng v khin my nng nhanh, gy gim hiu sut. Mt s du hiu cho thy, laptop cn thay keo tn nhit nh sau:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Laptop chy nng bt thng d khng dng tc v nng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Qut tn nhit hot ng lin tc vi ting n ln.</li>\r\n 	<li>My t ng tt khi chi game hoc dng phn mm nng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBn nn thay keo tn nhit nh k t 12 nm/ln ti trung tm k thut c kinh nghim  m bo.\r\n<h3 id=\"dau-hieu-laptop-can-ve-sinh-ve-trong\"><strong>Du hiu laptop cn v sinh v trong</strong></h3>\r\nNu gp cc du hiu di y, laptop ca bn c th ang cn c v sinh phn cng bn trong:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li