if;\"><strong>Hng x l:</strong>Ngi dng nn th sc bng cp v c sc chnh hng khc  loi tr li ph kin. Nu vn khng ln, cn mang my n trung tm sa cha  kim tra pin, IC ngun v mainboard, sau  thay th linh kin hng nu cn.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Gi dao ng:</strong>450.000  2.000.000 VN, ty nguyn nhn xut pht t pin, IC ngun hay hng main.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"pin-phong%2C-nong-bat-thuong\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Pin phng, nng bt thng</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Pin l b phn d xung cp sau mt thi gian di s dng. Trng hp pin b phng hoc nng bt thng khng ch gy kh chu m cn tim n nguy c chy n.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cap-cuu-dien-thoai-5.jpg\" alt=\"Pin phng, nng bt thng\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Du hiu:</strong></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Mt lng hoc mn hnh b i ln do pin phng</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">My nng nhanh khi sc hoc s dng</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Thi lng pin gim mnh, thm ch t sp ngun khi ang dng.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Hng x l:</strong>Cn thay pin mi chnh hng hoc pin dung lng chun. ng thi kim tra thm IC sc v bo mch  loi b nguyn nhn gy nng bt thng.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Gi dao ng:</strong>350.000  1.500.000 VN, ty dng my v dung lng pin.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"loi-phan-mem%2C-treo-logo%2C-mat-du-lieu\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Li phn mm, treo logo, mt d liu</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ngoi h hng phn cng, in thoi cng c th gp cc vn  lin quan n phn mm. Mt s li ph bin nh treo logo khi khi ng, chy chm, t khi ng li hoc mt d liu,....</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cap-cuu-dien-thoai-6.jpg\" alt=\"Li phn mm, treo logo, mt d liu\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Du hiu:</strong></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">My b treo logo khi bt ngun, lin tc reset</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Thao tc chm, ng dng hay b thot t ngt</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Khng truy cp c d liu trong b nh.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Hng x l:</strong>Thc hin chy li phn mm, ci t li h iu hnh, qut virus hoc khi phc ci t gc. Trng hp mt d liu quan trng, cn s dng dch v cu d liu chuyn su.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Gi dao ng:</strong>200.000  1.500.000 VN, ph thuc vo mc  li v nhu cu khi phc d liu.</span>\r\n<h2 id=\"cac-buoc-cap-cuu-dien-thoai-tam-thoi-tai-nha\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Cc bc cp cu in thoi tm thi ti nh</strong></span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Khi in thoi gp s c bt ng, vic x l kp thi v ng cch ti nh s gip hn ch h hng nng hn trc khi mang n trung tm sa cha. Di y l nhng bc cp cu c bn m ngi dng nn thc hin:</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"tat-may-ngay-khi-gap-su-co\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Tt my ngay khi gp s c</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Khi in thoi b ri, va p, dnh nc hoc xut hin li bt thng, vic u tin cn lm l tt ngun ngay lp tc. iu ny gip ngn chn tnh trng chp mch, trnh cho linh kin bn trong b tn hi nng hn.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cap-cuu-dien-thoai-7.jpg\" alt=\"Tt ngun bc cp cu in thoi tm thi ti nh u tin\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Nhiu ngi thng c gng bt li my  kim tra, nhng hnh ng ny c th khin in thoi hng nng hn.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"thao-sim%2C-the-nho-de-bao-ve-du-lieu\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Tho SIM, th nh  bo v d liu</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">SIM v th nh cha nhiu d liu quan trng nh s lin lc, tin nhn, hnh nh, ti liu. Khi in thoi gp s c, bn nn tho ngay hai b phn ny  trnh mt d liu. y l bc n gin nhng rt hu ch, c bit trong trng hp my h hng nng v cn nhiu thi gian sa cha.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"lau-kho-(neu-bi-uot)%2C-khong-dung-may-say\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Lau kh (nu b t), khng dng my sy</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Nu in thoi b ri xung nc hoc dnh ma, hy lau kh b mt ngoi bng khn mm. Sau , t my  ni thong mt  nc thot ra t nhin.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/cap-cuu-dien-thoai-8.jpg\" alt=\"Lau kh (nu b t), khng dng my sy\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Tuyt i khng nn dng my sy tc hoc phi di nh nng gt. Bi v nhit  cao c th lm hng bo mch, pin v mn hnh bn trong.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"khong-tu-y-thao-may-neu-khong-co-ky-nang\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Khng t  tho my nu khng c k nng</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Nhiu ngi ngh rng t tho my  hong kh hoc kim tra linh kin s gip tit kim chi ph. Tuy nhin, nu khng c k nng chuyn mn, bn c th lm gy cp kt ni, hng socket hoc lm mt kh nng chng nc ca my. Do , ch nn x l phn bn ngoi, tuyt i khng can thip su vo phn cng.</span>', 'Cp cu in thoi nhanh chng, uy tn, gi tt', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '134-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-09-02 16:24:54', '2025-09-02 16:24:54', '', 134, 'http://localhost/ekart/?p=135', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
