(160, 1, '2025-09-04 00:50:40', '2025-09-04 00:50:40', '<h2 id=\"ios-18-bi-nong-may-co-nhung-dau-hieu-nao%3F\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>iOS 18 b nng my c nhng du hiu no?</strong></span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>iOS 18 b nng my</strong>khng phi lc no cng d nhn bit. Di y l mt s du hiu ph bin xc nh \'d yu\' ca bn c ang \'qu nhit\':</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Mt lng iPhone nng r rt, c bit l khu vc camera, khin kh cm nm thoi mi.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">iPhone hot ng chm chp, ng dng phn hi  ch, thm ch b treo hoc .</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Pin b hao rt nhanh do CPU v GPU lm vic  gii quyt cc tc v nng.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"> bo v thit b, iOS c th t ng gim  sng mn hnh khi my qu nng.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Mn hnh c th xut hin cnh bo nng, yu cu ngi dng tt bt tnh nng hoc  iPhone ngh.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/ios-18-bi-nong-may-1.jpg\" alt=\"iOS 18 b nng my c nhng du hiu no?\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Nu nhn thy cc du hiu trn, bn cn c bin php x l ph hp  bo v iPhone.</span>\r\n<h2 id=\"nguyen-nhan-ios-18-bi-nong-may\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Nguyn nhn iOS 18 b nng my</strong></span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Khi iPhone gp phi tnh trng nng my, chc chn c mt s nguyn nhn c bn ng sau. iOS 18 d c nhiu tnh nng mi, cng khng trnh khi nhiu vn  phin phc. Nhng vn  ny i hi ngi dng phi hiu v khc phc nhanh chng  bo v thit b:</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"loi-phan-mem-tren-ios-18\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Li phn mm trn iOS 18</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Mt trong nhng nguyn nhn hng u khin iOS 18 b nng my l li phn mm. iOS 18 l mt phin bn mi v c th cha c ti u ha hon ton. iu ny c bit ng vi nhng ngi dng phin bn beta.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/ios-18-bi-nong-may-2.jpg\" alt=\"Nguyn nhn iOS 18 b nng my\" width=\"840\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Cc li phn mm nh xung t gia ng dng v h iu hnh thng gy tnh trng qu ti. Mt s tnh nng mi cha hon thin cng c th tiu tn nhiu ti nguyn, lm my nng.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">ng dng khng tng thch hoc gp li khi chy trn nn iOS 18 cng l nguyn nhn qu nhit. Khi ng dng xung t vi h iu hnh, CPU phi x l nhiu nhim v phc tp hn. Chnh v vy, vic cp nht v v li lin tc cho iOS 18 l rt cn thit.</span>\r\n<h3 id=\"su-dung-thoi-gian-dai\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>S dng thi gian di</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">S dng iPhone trong thi gian di m khng ngh ngi cng l nguyn nhn khin my b nng. Khi bn chi game nng, xem phim di tp hoc livestream, chip x l phi hot ng lin tc. iu ny dn n tnh trng my nng do CPU v GPU hot ng ht cng sut.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://image.dienthoaivui.com.vn/x,webp,q90/https://dashboard.dienthoaivui.com.vn/uploads/dashboard/editor_upload/ios-18-bi-nong-may-3.